{
  "texts": [
    "Tuzoff et al. [34] utilized the Faster R-CNN model for tooth detection and the VGG-16 Net model for tooth numbering on panoramic radiographs.",
    "The CNN-based models demonstrated high recall and specificity values for teeth detection and numbering tasks, comparable to experts.",
    "However, their model exhibited misclassifications in cases where a tooth was missing, whereas our improved model accurately detected these cases.",
    "Image samples for these cases are given in Fig. 11.A DL method Faster R-CNN proposed for tooth detection and numbering in periapical radiographs by Chen et al.",
    "In order to improve the detection accuracy, they proposed three post-processing techniques to complement the baseline Faster R-CNN."
  ]
}